This is a note, written by a crude, goblin hand.
"This be all the gold that be left from getting ogres to join army. If the Master wants us to hire more things, like a barbarian tribe or a dragon, we gonna need more gold! This might buy more goblins, but Master not seem real impressed with us so far.
Um... and ogres smashed Bedzil to jelly, so now me gonna need new partner."
